This directory contains the Tcl library datatable, which help manipulating and
formatting data shaped into tables.

More information in doc subdirectory:

| datatable.um.texinfo    | user manual                                    |
| datatable.um.fr.texinfo | manuel utilisateur                             |
| datatable.teaser.org    | quick introduction of abilities of the modules |
| datatable.dg.texinfo    | developer guide                                |


